{"tid":1053504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，拜山要搭地鐵係咪有錯","createTime":"2019-03-09T06:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T08:18:17.000Z","uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f23acaf3fff902f7a3cef5bcad181d0142f827","tid":1053504,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，屋企年年臨到清明都拜山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先陪屋企人拜山，星期六中午多人出街是常識吧，咁我拎住祭品同衣包搭地鐵再轉綠色線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉緊綠色綠嗰陣，車入面係多人，但唔係迫到似返放工時間，啲人塞住門口就真，我開口叫唔該借借，點知塞住門口嗰個人唔理我（佢個樣唔蝗），諗住撞開佢，佢就頂返我出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞到成個月台得我一個要on99咁等下一班車，落車嗰陣仲俾屋企人屌，驚我整唔見啲祭品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老實實，拜山要搭地鐵係咪有錯，俾其他人以為我係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係好多人根本未拜過山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f8e52333e828a60f1516450c2fa11ca27ebe87","tid":1053504,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88940515c6ea82b5a5a4517fc8cea4234436639d","tid":1053504,"uid":198165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:29:04.000Z","msg":"錯在你冇閪，有閪你一早出左車"},{"pid":"1b6a0a837a92d95b4b3f20f2f741e49c142603f9","tid":1053504,"uid":198165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯在你冇閪，有閪你一早上左車</blockquote>"},{"pid":"41ad93e973c3bd96c8e275fa2466157f4d6b88bf","tid":1053504,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:30:57.000Z","msg":"咁你屋企人又上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af52fe425f0d317ebc6625b3f7f08d7d5933818","tid":1053504,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc